node.text: My favorite scenes are when @damsonidris & I get to face off. We share a lot of parallels with our characters when it comes to ambition, dedication & drive but unlike Franklin & Manboy we’re on the same team. Working together to bring you the best product every week! #SnowfallFX

node.text: My favorite scenes are when @damsonidris & I get to face off. We share a lot of parallels with our characters when it comes to ambition, dedication & drive but unlike Franklin & Manboy we’re on the same team. Working together to bring you the best product every week! #SnowfallFX

node.text:
@usvsbillieholiday is out Today on Hulu!
•
•
This is an amazing film! @leedaniels meticulously tells the all too common tale of the U.S. government using its full power to tear down our leaders, those willing to risk their lives to standup to a system built to keep us oppressed! @andradaymusic embodies Billie Holiday in a way we’ve never seen before, an absolute flawless performance. I’m so excited for her to receive the flowers she deserves because she put her soul into this film. I’m so proud of everyone involved & super blessed to have been a part of this exposé of American History.
